summary: This document is a filing from the United States Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York, containing defense and prosecution papers submitted in the Jeffrey Epstein case. It appears to be correspondence transmitting legal documents.

events.title: Filing of Epstein Case Papers
events.description: Defense and prosecution legal papers were filed in the Jeffrey Epstein case.

keyFacts: Legal papers were filed in the Jeffrey Epstein case on July 16, 2019.
The filing includes documents from both the defense and the prosecution.
The United States Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York was involved in the filing.
The document is part of the official court record in the Epstein case.
